       VALUES (
        '5-features-acme-ideal-solar-roofing-canvassers','usr_admin_demo','a7516e85f960f410769f4b2cd289c15c623bbd1795cdffd45f094e22d4464b40',NULL,'urn:contentforge-seed:5-features-acme-ideal-solar-roofing-canvassers','5 Features That Make Acme the Definitive Choice','/blog/5-features-acme-ideal-solar-roofing-canvassers',
        'Guides','Article','4 min read','5 Features Ready for Solar & Roofing Canvassers | Acme','Explore the core roofing features: smart multi-pin overlays, live tracking, instant lead assignment, offline routing, and customized pitch flow.',
        'Built for the Field, Not the Boardroom','["Smart Territory & Pin Drop: eliminate double knocks with color-coded, labeled result pins.","GPS tracking & squad metrics keep operations transparent while boosting rep coaching.","Instant lead capture sync gets warm homeowner files straight into inside sales queues.","Full offline functionality works in dead spots and updates automatically when reconnected."]','When you''re out knocking in the Texas heat or freezing winds, you don''t need a bloated desktop CRM. Acme is optimized for extreme field usability, turning quick clicks into accurate data folders.',NULL,NULL,0,'2026-05-22T09:50:48.142Z','2026-05-22T09:50:48.142Z');
